title: Jankovic, Stosur advance to quarterfinals at Hong Kong Open
text: Photo: Kin Cheung, AP Samantha Stosur of Australia returns a shot against Monica Puig of Puerto Rica during the second round match at the WTA Hong Kong Open tennis tournament in Hong Kong, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015. Samantha Stosur of Australia returns a shot against Monica Puig of... HONG KONG (AP) — Jelena Jankovic and Samantha Stosur advanced to the quarterfinals of the Hong Kong Open on Wednesday, both winning in straight sets.
